---
title: Roast Chicken & Prosciutto Greens for Dinner with Burnt Basque Cheesecake for Dessert
description: Get ready to elevate your dining experience with this mouthwatering feast. Succulent chicken is roasted to juicy perfection and paired with a luscious peppercorn-spiked hollandaise. Finish things off on a sweet note with a dreamy slice of basque cheesecake, drizzled with a sweet and tart sauce.

